text: My Kitchen Rules SA is a South African reality television show based on the popular Australian reality television series My Kitchen Rules. The show premiered in South Africa on M-Net in 2017. In 2019, My Kitchen Rules SA won the SAFTA for Best International Format Show. ==References == Category:Food reality television series Category:South African reality television series Category:2010s South African television series Category:2017 South African television series debuts
